# Caddy reverse proxy for the fashion-monitor web app.
# Caddy terminates TLS (auto-HTTPS via Let's Encrypt for a public domain, or a
# local self-signed cert for `localhost`) and forwards to the dashboard service.
#
# Set WEB_DOMAIN in .env. For a public host this triggers automatic HTTPS.
{$WEB_DOMAIN} {
	encode gzip
	reverse_proxy dashboard:3030
}
